Although it's possible to set the permissions so that a given user can add or remove comments from the space, it would be nice if you could indicate that some/all users are allowed to remove their OWN comments from the space.  It's a minor difference, but I don't want all users to remove all comments, but would prefer it users could remove their own if they so desired.

